S3 Classes

ready4use_distributions()

ready4 S3 class for list object that summarises the parameters of each distribution

ready4use_dataverses()

ready4 S3 class for tibble object lookup table of files to be imported from a dataverse.

ready4use_imports()

ready4 S3 class for tibble object lookup table of sources of raw (un-processed) data to import.

ready4use_mapes()

ready4 S3 class for tibble object that stores simulation structural parameters relating to Mean Absolute Prediction Errors.

ready4use_dictionary()

ready4 s3 class defining a data dictionary tibble.

ready4use_manifest()

ready4 s3 class defining a manifest of data required to create an R package.
